<event name="JUBJUB_QUEST" unique="true">
    <beaconType id="map_icon_jubjub_quest" global="true">
        <color r="95" g="103" b="45" a="1.0"/>
        <unvisitedTooltip>This is the Moon (JUBJUB is here!!!)</unvisitedTooltip>
    </beaconType>
	<text></text>
    <img planet="PLANET_POPULATED_MOON_JUB"/>
    <choice hidden="true">
		<text>Land on The Moon.</text>
		<event>
			<text>Humans of this era assume Luna is uninhabited but you can see some strange mouse-like creatures wandering the surface of the planet. </text>
            <choice>
                <text>Approach the creatures and attempt to communicate.</text> <!--CHOICE: STANDARD QUEST-->
                <event>
                    <text>text</text>
                </event>
            </choice>
            <choice req="jubjub">
                <text>(JubJub) Whistle to greet the creatures</text> <!--CHOICE: JUBJUB ON BOARD-->
                <event>
                    <text>ADD INFO PLS</text>
                </event>
            </choice>
            <choice hidden="true"> <!--CHOICE: IGNORE QUEST-->
                <text>Leave.</text>
                <event/>
            </choice>
        </event>
    </choice>
    <choice>
        <text>Ignore The Moon</text>
        <event>
            <text>You decide not to risk landing.</text>
            <choice>
                <text>Do something onboard the ship.</text>
                <event load="STORAGE_CHECK"/>
            </choice>
            <choice>
                <text>Do nothing.</text>
                <event/>
            </choice>
        </event>
    </choice>
</event>


<event name="JUBJUB_MOON" unique="false">
    <beaconType id="map_icon_jubjub_quest" global="true">
        <color r="95" g="103" b="45" a="1.0"/>
        <unvisitedTooltip>This is the Moon (JUBJUB is here!!!)</unvisitedTooltip>
    </beaconType>
	<text>You've discovered a small celestial body that seems to be very familar, although you're not normally this close. It's Luna, more often referred to as The Moon: Earth's only natural satellite.</text>
    <img planet="PLANET_POPULATED_MOON_JUB"/>
    <choice hidden="true">
        <text>Land on the Moon</text>
        <event>
            <text>Humans of this era assume Luna is uninhabited but you can see some strange mouse-like creatures wandering the surface of the planet.</text>
            <choice>
                <text>Approach the creatures and attempt to communicate.</text>
                <event>
                    <text>While the creatures speak only in whistles, they seem to be able to understand you.</text>
						<event load="CLANGER_ENCOUNTER"/>
                </event>
            </choice>
            <choice hidden="true" req="jubjub">
                <text>(JubJub) Whistle to greet the creatures</text>
                <event load="JUBJUB_RETURNS"/>
            </choice>
            <choice hidden="true" req="soviet">
                <text>(Soviet) Send your Soviet crewmember to communicate.</text>
                <event>
                    <text>Your crewmember cautiously approaches and says, "Hello strrrange crrreaturrres, ve mean you niet harrrm. Ve arrre herrre to learrrn."
While the creatures speak only in whistles, they seem to be able to understand you.</text>
                        <event load="CLANGER_ENCOUNTER"/>
                </event>
            </choice>
            <choice>
                <text>Leave.</text>
                <event>
                    <text>You decide not to communicate and return to your ship.</text>
                    <choice>
                        <text>Do something onboard the ship.</text>
                        <event load="STORAGE_CHECK"/>
                    </choice>
                    <choice>
                        <text>Do nothing.</text>
                        <event/>
                    </choice>
                </event>
            </choice>
        </evemt>
    </choice>
    <choice hidden="true">
        <text>Ignore the Moon</text>
        <event>
            <text>You ignore the moon.</text>
            <choice>
                <text>Do something onboard the ship.</text>
                <event load="STORAGE_CHECK"/>
            </choice>
            <choice>
                <text>Do nothing.</text>
                <event/>
            </choice>
        </event>
    </choice>
</event>

<event name="CLANGER_ENCOUNTER">
    <text>The creatures look at you.</text>
    <choice hidden="true">
        <text>Explain your mission.</text>
        <event>
            <text>TESTING</text>
        </event>
    </choice>
    <choice hidden="true">
        <text>Ask if they have anything to sell.</text>
        <event>
            <text>TESTING2</text>
        </event>
    </choice>
    <choice hidden="true">
        <text>"Take me to your leader."</text>
        <event>
            <text>TESTING3</text>
        </event>
    </choice>
    <choice hidden="true" req="jubjub">
        <text>(JubJub) Whistle to greet the creatures</text>
        <event>
            <text>TESTING4</text>
        </event>
    </choice>
    <choice hidden="true" req="soviet">
        <text>(Soviet) Explain the importance of the Abolition of Private Property.</text>
        <event>
            <text>TESTING5</text>
        </event>
    </choice>
</event>

<event name="JUBJUB_RETURNS">
    <text>The creatures seem excited to see JubJub and rush over to greet you and your crew.

The leader of these creatures, who introduces himself as Major Clanger, approaches your captain and says, "We had a feeling you would arrive. It seems the Multiverse is spreading faster than we expected. I have someone I think you would like to meet."</text>
    <choice>
        <text>Follow Major Clanger to his burrow.</text>
        <event>
            <text>Once inside the burrow Major Clanger turns to you, "I would like you to meet my good friend, JubJub."</text>
            <choice>
                <text>Uh don't we already know him?</text>
                <event>
                    <text>The new JubJub looks at you with his ears dipping and his smile faltering, "Well thanks I guess.."</text>
                    <choice>
                        <text>Oh I didn't mean it like that sorry!</text>
                        <event>
                            <text>The new JubJub perks up a little bit and asks to join your crew.</text>
                            <choice>
                                <text>Continue...</text>
                                <event load="JUB_TO_JUB_INVITE"/>
                            </choice>
                        </event>
                    </choice>
                    <choice>
                        <text>I don't know what to tell you, one Jub is enough</text>
                        <event>
                            <text>Your crewmember looks sad and lets you know that now he has found another Jub he can't just leave them. (JubJub leaves your crew.)</text>
                            <removeCrew class="jubjub">
                                <clone>false</clone>
                                <text>You cannot clone your crew, as they are not dead.</text>
                            </removeCrew>
                        </event>
                    </choice>
                    <choice req="jubjub">
                        <text>(JubJub) Hey friend! Don't mind the captain, they're just like that sometimes.</text>
                        <event>
                            <text>The new JubJub perks up a little bit and asks to join your crew.</text>
                            <choice>
                                <text>Continue...</text>
                                <event load="JUB_TO_JUB_INVITE"/>
                            </choice>
                        </event>
                    </choice>
                </event>
            </choice>
            <choice>
                <text>This is getting out of hand! Now there are two of them!</text>
                <event>
                    <text>The new JubJub looks at you, smiles, and then exlaims, "She can't do that! Shoot her or something!"

He looks at you and asks if you would mind letting him join your crew.</text>
                    <choice>
                        <text>Continue...</text>
                        <event load="JUB_TO_JUB_INVITE"/>
                    </choice>
                </event>
            </choice>
            <choice>
                <text>Greetings Comrade</text>
                <event>
                    <text>The new JubJub looks at you and tilts his head. "Now, that's a name I haven't heard in a long time"
                    
He looks at you and asks if you would mind letting him join your crew.</text>
                    <choice>
                        <text>Continue...</text>
                        <event load="JUB_TO_JUB_INVITE"/>
                    </choice>
                </event>
            </choice>
            <choice req="jubjub">
                <text>(JubJub) ANOTHER JUB!!! Finally after all this time!!</text>
                <event>
                    <text>The new JubJub jumps up and down and then runs over to your crewmember and they begin speaking excitedly in a language that you are unable to understand.

It seems your crewmember has invited this new JubJub onto your crew.</text>
                    <choice>
                        <text>Continue...</text>
                        <event load="JUB_TO_JUB_INVITE"/>
                    </choice>
                </event>
            </choice>
        </event>
    </choice>
    <choice>
        <text>This is too weird. Return to your ship.</text>
        <event>
            <text>You return to your ship.</text>
            <choice>
                <text>Do something onboard the ship.</text>
                <event load="STORAGE_CHECK"/>
            </choice>
            <choice>
                <text>Do nothing.</text>
                <event/>
            </choice>
        </event>
    </choice>
</event>
<event name="JUB_TO_JUB_INVITE">
    <text>Both JubJubs look at you.</text>
    <choice>
        <text>Oh, we don't have space for you sorry.</text>
        <event>
            <text>Your crewmember looks sad and lets you know that now he has found another Jub he can't just leave them. (JubJub Leaves your Crew.)</text>
            <removeCrew class="jubjub">
                <clone>false</clone>
                <text>You cannot clone your crew, as they are not dead.</text>
			</removeCrew>
        </event>
    </choice>
    <choice>
        <text>Welcome aboard! </text>
        <event>
            <crewMember amount="1" class="jubjub">JubJub</crewMember>
        </event>
    </choice>
</event>

